      • getPropertyMappingFromFile

        public static PropertyMapping getPropertyMappingFromFile(String folder,
                                                         String name)
        Get propertyMapping from a file with the same name as the LIMES config file without ".xml" concateneted with "propertymatch". Content should be lines Source Property \t Target Property \t {"number", "string"}. E.g. "dbo:name refs:label string".
        Parameters:
        folder - Path of the folder
        name - Name of the LIMES config file.
        Returns:
        PropertyMapping read from the file.
